OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FHow Giving Tuesday became a
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fglobal phenomenon          
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, More than 80 countries from around the 
OL,6, world are expected to join this year's 
OL,7, Giving Tuesday, when acts of "radical  
OL,8, generosity" are encouraged.            
OL,10,FThe growing global phenomenon takes    
OL,11,Fplace each year on the first Tuesday   
OL,12,Fafter US Thanksgiving.                 
OL,14,FGivingTuesday, the non-profit that     
OL,15,Fcreated the movement in 2012, says     
OL,16,Fevery act of generosity counts.        
OL,18,FIt tracked a record $2.7bn (#2.2bn)    
OL,19,Fdonated by 35 million people on Giving 
OL,20,FTuesday in the US last year.           
